Installation
====================

This project provides the visualization of mechanical systems. It needs, beside other tools:
- mbxmlutils
- hdf5serie
- Coin, get it at https://github.com/coin3d/coin, see build instructions at https://github.com/coin3d/coin/wiki/BuildWithCMake
- SoQt, get it at https://github.com/coin3d/soqt, see build instructions at https://github.com/coin3d/coin/wiki/BuildWithCMake
- libqwt6. The program will NOT work with libqwt5.
- ...


1. Checkout from git
--------------------

If not already done, checkout the git tree
# git clone https://github.com/mbsim-env/openmbv.git


2. Run AutoTools
----------------

# aclocal
# autoheader
# libtoolize -c --force
# autoconf
# automake -a -c --force


3. Proceed with configure
-------------------------

See file INSTALL.
